      info home http://bitmath.org/code/mtdev/
      desc 'library converts kernel MT events to slotted type B protocol
The mtdev is a stand-alone library which transforms
all variants of kernel MT events to the slotted type B protocol.
The events put into mtdev may be from any MT device,
specifically type A without contact tracking,
type A with documentation for further details.'
